          "process_md": "**Step 1:** Visit the nearest Anganwadi Centre (AWC) in your locality.\n**Step 2:** Obtain the scheme enrollment form from the Anganwadi Worker (AWW).\n**Step 3:** Fill in the details in the form with attach the required documents.\n**Step 4:** Submit the filled form and documents to the AWC.\n> **After Submission of Application:**\n\n\n- The Anganwadi Worker verifies the eligibility and registers the applicant under MSPY – Maternal Nutrition.\n- Beneficiary receives acknowledgement of enrolment and is included in the monthly THR distribution list.\n- On the 1st of every month, the AWW distributes the entitled THR packages (Til Ladoo, Chana, Paushtik Bhel, Dates) at the AWC.\n- Health services such as ANC check-ups, IFA and Calcium supplementation continue as per schedule.\n\n<br>\n\n"
        }
